---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-gray-800 text-gray-300 mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-6">
      <!-- サイト情報 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-1">🐾 Pet Life Navi</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">ペットと暮らすすべての人へ、<br>役立つ情報をお届けします。</p>
        <a href="https://x.com/pet_navi_jp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
          @pet_navi_jp
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- リンク -->
      <nav class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm">
        <a href="/dog/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">🐶 犬の記事一覧</a>
        <a href="/cat/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">🐱 猫の記事一覧</a>
        <a href="/dog-care/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">🐾 犬のケア</a>
        <a href="/cat-care/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">🐾 猫のケア</a>
        <a href="/about/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">運営者情報</a>
        <a href="/privacy-policy/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">プライバシーポリシー</a>
        <a href="/profile/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">プロフィール</a>
        <a href="/disclaimer/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">免責事項</a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-700 mt-8 pt-6 text-xs text-gray-500 text-center space-y-1">
      <p>当サイトはアフィリエイト広告を掲載しています。</p>
      <p>&copy; {year} Pet Life Navi. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
